Definition: a program that appears desirable but actually contains something harmful
Example: the contents of a trojan can be a virus or a worm; when he downloaded the free game it turned out to be a trojan horse
Synonyms: trojan_horse, malevolent_program, a, program, that, appears, desirable, but, actually, contains, something, harmful, the, contents, of, can, be, virus, or, worm, when, he, downloaded, free, game, it, turned, out, to, horse
Category: noun.communication
